billion. By JENNIFER MANN. Story will move in ``f'' category.
ENERGY-SAVINGS (Undated) A University of Kansas program has helped
manufacturers identify more than $25 million in energy and
production savings since it was founded in the early 1980s. By
STEVE EVERLY. Story will move in ``f'' category.
</P>
</TEXT>
