<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-07 13:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1789 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEW-HILLARY-BOS &LR;      07-07 1435
