   KOSOVO-HOUSES (Pec, Yugoslavia) _ A tale of two houses, one
belonging to ethnic Albanians who came home to find sinister
calling cards left by Serb paramilitaries; the other a Serb
apartment taken over by an Albanian family who said they had
nowhere else to go. By Susan Milligan.
