   NEW-HILLARY (Washington) _ This will be a very different first
lady, juggling White House roles and running a Senate campaign. Not
only will she be surrounded by Secret Service agents, but she'll
also be attending dinners to get votes and raise money. By Mary
Leonard. By Mary Leonard. 1485 words.
